OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fand very warm through the evening with
OL,7,Fsome late sunshine. Skies remaining
OL,8,Fclear overnight with light winds.
OL,9,FAnother very warm and muggy night to
OL,10,Fcome.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FLots of sunshine and feeling
OL,13,Feven hotter with extreme heat
OL,14,Fcontinuing and high humidity. A risk
OL,15,Fof intense thunderstorms later with
OL,16,Fstrong gusty winds and a sudden change
OL,17,Fin temperature.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
