OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FAnother
OL,6,Fhot day on Friday, with temperatures
OL,7,Fslowly coming down through the
OL,8,Fweekend. Lots of dry and sunny
OL,9,Fweather, but a risk of some
OL,10,Fthunderstorms at times.
